games.instructions: The objective of the game is to control a small worm that needs to feed but be careful that the soldiers and the army think about destroying you. Now you can play this new game evolve your monster and become the best monster in the world.

games.description: It seems a simple problem, but it is often not that simple! Quickly answer the questions on the screen, the answer is in the picture! Do you want to change your mind? Maybe there will be a different effect!
games.instructions: Tap to play.

Be careful, there are balls everywhere, you may not be able to complete the level at any time. watch out for monsters, they are everywhere.
games.instructions: "Z" Jump + "Arrow key" Move / Mobile Touch Control

games.description: Perfect Tongue is a casual decompression game. In the game, you need to eat more food with your long tongue, but don't eat dangerous props. You need to avoid these dangerous props to make sure that you can finish eating quickly, and there are many roads for you to use.
games.instructions: Tap to play.

games.description: Flat Jewels Match 3 is classic match 3 game in modern flat design. Enjoy well known game mechanics in this simple yet addictive version. Select either Levels mode or Time Attack gameplay mode. In Levels mode you will go through 150 levels fulfilling simple tasks. In Time Attack mode you will aim to reach highest possible score in limited time.
games.instructions: Swap gems to create rows and columns of three or more.

games.description: Defeat the Red King by strategically moving your pieces to get to the Red King's location. There are 24 challenging levels in this game where you'll sometimes need to slide the gameboard halves or use the gravity switcher squares. No time limit in this game so you can take your time and if you get stuck on a level you can always click the Video button on the Main Menu to see the walkthrough video. You don't need to know how to play chess as the chess pieces in this game will display the squares they can move to when they are clicked. In fact this can be a good introduction as to how chess pieces move!
games.instructions: Click on one of your blue chess pieces to highlight where it can move. To move the piece to a highlighted square, click on that square. To complete a level you'll need to move one of your blue pieces to the square the Red King occupies. More detailed instructions as well as a walkthrough video are available in the game via the buttons on the Main Menu.

games.description: Among Stacky Runner is an adventure game where you have to collect yellow blocks in order to overcome the stairs and various obstacles. You can build a ladder from the blocks you collected using the left click button. In Among Stacky Runner, it is necessary to use the blocks you have sparingly in order to move on to the next level. Play the Among Stacky Runner game to get the highest score by reaching the top.
games.instructions: Use blocks to pass obstacles.

games.description: This game is an educational game for the kids. They can play and learn about pictures like fruits, vegetables, animals, food, fish, birds, robots, and more... Drag and drop the matching image into the box. Enjoy!
games.instructions: Drag and drop the matching image into the box.

games.description: Have fun with this new casual game go as far as you can show that you can with infinite games full of deadly obstacles !!!! Play Geometry Neon Dash Rainbow now totally free and enjoy many hours of entertainment.
games.instructions: The objective of the game is to control the small square character to take him as far as possible in a colorful world but make no mistake, it is not as easy as it sounds, on your infinite path you will not be able to stop and you will find thousands of dangerous objects. Accumulate the most points and improve with each attempt, you can unlock new characters and levels as you evolve.

games.description: Do you miss the fun and addictive game 4 Colors Classic? Or have you never played this great game? Then go ahead, choose a character and take part in wonderful friendly competitions. A perfectly recreated atmosphere of the game, detailed instructions, simple controls and many interesting opponents who are ready at any time to keep your company are waiting for you.
games.instructions: Choose the numbers of players. Match cards by color or number and be the first to get rid of them. Action cards run the game. Next player in sequence draws two cards and misses a turn. Skip card stops the player. Reverse card switches the direction of the turn to the opposite. Wild card can be places on any card at any time and allows you to change the color of the card. The wild draw four is a special card, allows you to change the color of the card and forces the next player to pick 4 cards.

games.description: Hello from the 3 series of kingdom of ninja game. Kingdom of ninja 3 game, which consists of 15 different levels, will challenge you. If you want to join this adventure, what are you waiting for?
games.instructions: "Z" Jump + "Arrow key" Move / Mobile Touch Control

games.description: Candy Burst, an iconic Match 3 puzzle game offering you great gaming experience filled with relaxation and fun. Swap and match Candies in dazzling combinations to complete the challenging levels. Have Fun is this epic Match three match game!
games.instructions: swipe to match candies

games.description: You need to collect all the coins at every level. There are two modes in game: the platforming mode, in which you can run and jump, and the sokoban mode, in which you can move blocks, coins, etc. In sokoban mode chests monsters wake up, attack and chase the main character. In platforming mode chests sleep and can be used as platforms.

games.description: Balls Maze is a classic puzzle game, perfect for taking a quick break to train your brain. It’s designed to be a surprisingly simple solo game played by swiping through fun 2D retro labyrinths and popping balloons. Smash all the balloons in the maze and you will win!!!
games.instructions: Touch and drag to rotate the level.

games.description: Simple one-button football game with cute dogs. Kick ball when it is right on crosshair and score goals. Get as high score as possible within 30 seconds time limit.
games.instructions: Kick ball when it is right on crosshair. Get bonus time for precise kicks.

games.description: Explore continent of Africa as a tourist and become familiar with its different countries and tourism attractions. During your long travel, you visit 15 different countries in Africa. Each country is considered as a level and in it, you will become familiar with that country’s name, flag, coat of arms, capital, official language and one of its most famous tourism attractions.
games.instructions: Touch on mobile device or keyboard and mouse on PC.

games.description: Place the pieces into board. Once you fill in a vertical or horizontal line, it will disappear, freeing up space for new pieces. Game will be over if there are no space for any the given blocks below the board.
games.instructions: Tips For Beginners. Drag wooden blocks into the 10×10 grid. Remove blocks by creating complete lines vertically or horizontally. Clear as multiple blocks at once as possible. Don't forget to use props. No space to stack blocks, the game is over.

games.description: Manage your small 10x10 field. Grow various crops and harvest it. Be smart when placing new seedings, so you never run out of space. Complete rows and columns to harvest it. When you fill up the truck, it will drive to market.
games.instructions: Drag and drop shapes from bottom area into main field view.

games.description: This is a 10 in 1 game with Olympic athletic sports such as Dash (100, 400 and 800 meters), Longjump, Highjump, Javelin, Hurdles, Pole vault, Discus, Shot pot.
games.instructions: Touch in the buttons in the screen to run and jump/throw or use your keyboard (Arrows and keys 'A' and 'D')

games.description: Open the gates to the world of letters in WordCube and give your vocabulary skills a workout! There are 4 game modes where you need to rearrange the letters and find the hidden words to get points!
games.instructions: WordCube is a fun puzzle game and all you need is your mouse to play this game. Choose between four different game modes and press the left click to rearrange the letters and search the cube for words.

games.description: Deer Hunter 2D is a fun sniper game where you hunt deers. You can play 30 fun levels in a great shooting gameplay. Play Deer Hunter now for an amazing hunter experience.
games.instructions: Tap to play

games.description: Water Sort Puzzle is a simple, fun and addictive sort puzzle game.Your next task is to sort the colored water in the cup until all the colors in the glass are the same. The game is easy to get used to, but it is difficult to become an expert and there are 1000 puzzles to challenge you.A challenging yet relaxing game to train your brain!
games.instructions: Touch any glass bottle to pour water into another bottle.The rule is that you can only pour water into another bottle if it is linked to the same color and there is enough space on the glass bottle.Do your best and don't get stuck. Don't worry, you can always start over at any time. Or use the help to add a new message.

games.description: Grow your sky farm empire and be a high tech billionaire in this idle farming game.Grow lettuce, strawberry, watermelon, lavender, mint, carrots, tomatoes and even GINSENG, in the sky! The FUTURE is HERE.Use the coins to upgrade your operations.Hire sophisticated managers to automate your tasks.Build new sky farms, high in the sky.Earn money while you sleep, from your Food Empire.Attract investors to your sky farm venture business, and cash out with tons of profit.
games.instructions: Tap on your lab workers to start farming.Next, transport the harvest to ground level with an elevator.Finally, transport the harvest to your warehouse to earn a profit.

games.description: Become the superior life form by defeating other players in Impostor.io! This game is inspired by Among Us and features similar visuals and controls. The gameplay is completely different: no need to worry about sneaking and pretending. The curtains are down, it’s every man (or alien) for himself. Beat everyone up with various weapons and climb to the top of the leader boards. Collect energy cubes to level up and become stronger. Can you survive the battle and become the most powerful impostor in the universe?
games.instructions: Control the character by moving the mouse cursor. The direction is indicated by the arrow hovering over the screen. Click LMB to attack and RMB to speed up. Running too often will drain your stamina, preventing you from leveling up. Sometimes it is necessary to avoid a confrontation with a stronger player. Your life consists of several segments – that’s the number of hits you can take. If you are low on health, look for more cubes – upgrading will rejuvenate you.

games.description: Happy Trucks is a filling puzzle game. Your job is to fill up the trucks with liquid. Do that in all 30 levels. For each level there is a different truck, so you need to estimate how much fluid will fit in that truck. You should not overfill the truck, nor should it be half empty. If you make a mistake in the assessment you will start playing that level again. Very interesting game that you will enjoy playing.
games.instructions: Tap on the screen to play this game.

games.description: Pop It Fidget NOW is a very fun and relaxing game. To unlock all figures, you must pop all bubbles in each level. Have fun touching all the bubbles, swapping colors and swapping sounds. Relax while having fun!

games.description: Philatelic Escape - Fauna Album 4 is the 4nd episode of series of games about stamp collector. Walk across the room, click on the items you see on the screen, collect them and use to solve the puzzles.Open the shelves and look for clues for cracking numeric and letter codes. The keys, postage stamps and other items that you are looking for could be hidden in anywhere, so be sure to check every single corner. Use logical thinking, creativity and your brains to solve all puzzles and find 10 stamps.

games.description: Have fun with this spectacular new game Sniper Trigger Revenge enjoy this game on kiz10.com totally free !!! If you like shooting games this game is ideal for you. Help the little stickman who needs your help to aim and shoot the little criminals who escaped from prison and refuse to return.
games.instructions: The objective of the game is to eliminate the different enemies in each level to complete the 15 missions of the game, but be careful that it is not as easy as it seems you must aim well to calculate the rebound of your bullets and not hurt the innocent who are in each level of the game. Try to use the objects around the map to hit the fugitives and keep the innocent safe. Have fun with this new exclusive game from kiz10.com

Gradually, the speed of the game is increased to make it more difficult. Let’s show everyone how good you are at soccer!

You have unlimited time to do this. Just slide the boxes and find the best way to escape with block with star.You can play in 25 levels, they are all different and some of them are real hard.

games.description: Play Freecell Solitaire, a web version of the most popular solitaire game in the world. If you are a solitaire enthusiast this is the perfect game for you!

games.description: Manage your restaurant by attending to customers, table management, taking orders and serving food. Collect the cash and move on to the next level! Earn maximum money by selecting the right table and right action at the right time. Showcase your time management skills.
games.instructions: Tap to select the customers, Tap to select the table and take orders. When the food is ready, serve and collect cash. Happy restaurant running!

games.description: The energy system is in danger. Control the Power Ball, collect energy points and charge the port in the middle. Enemy energies want to stop you. The Power Ball can be protected by several energy discharges. Each time you charge the port, you gain points that will improve the port, unlock it and improve other protection functions. The yellow line below shows the charge status of the Power Ball. Blue line supply of defensive discharges.
games.instructions: Click on the place where the Power Ball is to be moved. Defensive discharges and charging of the port are performed by a single red button at the bottom right. You can access the unlocked port auxiliary functions with the three buttons on the left. If you're playing on a computer, you can press the space bar instead of clicking the red button. Auxiliary port functions then in the game release keys 1, 2, 3 (not on numpad). The yellow and blue lines show the state of energy and discharges.
